@startuml name
title RANAL - Architektura systemu (zobecnena verze)

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Uzivatel" as user
component "Frontend\n(SPA / dashboard)" as fe

cloud "GitHub API" as gh
database "PostgreSQL" as db
folder "Lokalni git mirror" as repo
artifact "Logy / monitoring data" as logs

package "RANAL Backend (Rust, modularni monolit)" as be {
  component "Vstupni vrstva\n(ingest, sync trigger, validace)" as input
  component "Agregacni vrstva\n(transformace, business pravidla, backfill)" as agg
  component "Ulozna vrstva\n(repozitare, transakce, SQL dotazy)" as store
  component "Prezentacni vrstva\n(REST API + OpenAPI docs)" as api
}

' Frontend flow
user --> fe : prace s aplikaci
fe --> api : HTTP REST (dotazy na data)
api --> store : cteni/agregovane dotazy
store --> db : SELECT/INSERT/UPDATE

' Sync/ingest flow
input --> gh : nacteni PR/issues/users
input --> repo : analyza zmenenych souboru
input --> agg : predani surovych dat
agg --> store : ulozeni normalizovanych udalosti
agg --> logs : metriky + chyby + trvani
api --> logs : request/error logy

note right of be
  Backend je jeden deployable celek
  s internim delenim do vrstev.
end note

@enduml
